    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LockYourDoor</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《LockYourDoor》是一款全新的生存恐怖游戏，支持1至4人游玩。你的目标是生存并寻找失踪的好友达尔文。只有耐心和聪明的人才能在这场噩梦中生存下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/f51a510b6cb672c26d391162f5bf1f56.poster.avif?t=1766769744\" width=614 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/f51a510b6cb672c26d391162f5bf1f56.webm?t=1766769744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/f51a510b6cb672c26d391162f5bf1f56.mp4?t=1766769744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/8bf789a1253e4040a7105e4076b095af.avif?t=1766769744\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras_big/8bf789a1253e4040a7105e4076b095af.avif?t=1766769744 width=800 height=60 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于游戏</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1-4人在线合作</strong><br>作为最多4名幸存者的一组，你将探索周围的环境并面对各种威胁。揭开真相并共同制定策略。互相支持以生存下去。（还是选择背叛？你不需要死，你的朋友可以代替你去死!）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>具有挑战性的玩法</strong> <br>随着时间的推移，更多的威胁会出现，而你微弱的光芒会更快地消失。遵循达尔文的指引，适应新的情况。聪明地思考，并谨慎规划下一步行动。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/d1b2d86920804f8daf685ff37a637b19.webp?t=1766769744\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/d1b2d86920804f8daf685ff37a637b19.poster.webp?t=1766769744\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=234 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/8bf789a1253e4040a7105e4076b095af.avif?t=1766769744\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras_big/8bf789a1253e4040a7105e4076b095af.avif?t=1766769744 width=800 height=60 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>锁好你的门</strong><br>每位玩家将找到不同房间的钥匙。这些钥匙可用于为特定目的锁上或打开某些门。当夜晚降临时，玩家必须准备好面对黑暗中潜伏的恐怖噩梦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的人工智能</strong> <br>LockYourDoor包含多种人工智能，每种都有自己独特的特点、优势和弱点。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/81970b213549c7744d6a10a1ba14acdc.poster.avif?t=1766769744\" width=610 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/81970b213549c7744d6a10a1ba14acdc.webm?t=1766769744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/81970b213549c7744d6a10a1ba14acdc.mp4?t=1766769744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/8bf789a1253e4040a7105e4076b095af.avif?t=1766769744\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras_big/8bf789a1253e4040a7105e4076b095af.avif?t=1766769744 width=800 height=60 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>达尔文的笔记和日记</strong><br>遵循你的朋友达尔文的指引，在生存的同时寻找他留下的线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>物品与可重玩性</strong><br>LockYourDoor提供了多种物品，每种都有独特的用途。玩得越多，你就会越了解它们的使用方法，并学会有效利用它们。物品和钥匙的生成高度随机化，确保每一局游戏都与众不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>长时间且令人愉悦的游戏体验</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/943f6ca1c91a48b4d8f459f9dc1a79a5.webp?t=1766769744\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/943f6ca1c91a48b4d8f459f9dc1a79a5.poster.webp?t=1766769744\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=234 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras/8bf789a1253e4040a7105e4076b095af.avif?t=1766769744\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004140/extras_big/8bf789a1253e4040a7105e4076b095af.avif?t=1766769744 width=800 height=60 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>警告</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据开发者的说法，这款游戏可能包含以下内容，不适合所有年龄段或专业环境观看：暴力、血腥场面以及涉及成熟主题的内容。</p>",
